 >> DESCRIPTION:
==============================================================================

Add a LOGIN MATRIX to your Talisman BBS! This Luascript add-on will help you 
create your own unique experience for users to LOGIN or SIGNUP. 

Or - add your own functions using Talisman's built-in Lua support.

