 >> INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS (STEP-BY-STEP):
==============================================================================

1) Copy login.lua to your Talisman scripts directory (e.g. /bbs/scripts)

2) Copy art files to your Talisman gfiles directory (e.g. /bbs/gfiles)

3) Replace with your own art/matrix funcs, get creative!

Talisman will automatically execute login.lua if that file is present (FYI, you 
can also execute a script BEFORE login.lua using `prelogin.lua`).

